title: File:Receive Niceto Alcalá-Zamora at the harbor in Buenos Aires, 18.01.1942.jpg
author: José Luis Fernández de Castillejo Taviel de Andrade.
description: Federico Fernández de Castillejo with his daughter María Fernández de Castillejo Taviel de Andrade receives Niceto Alcalá-Zamora who appears with his daughters Pura and Isabel Alcalá-Zamora in dock C of the Port of Buenos Aires, Argentina, after they disembark the ship Herma Gorthon.
